name: Cambodian(6A Grade)
description:
Cambodian hair, which is becoming high demand more and more, has a slightly coarse texture and is a good match with freshly relaxed African American hair. Our Tress Up virgin Cambodian human hair is the highest quality and affordable prices on the market. 

The price is one bundle，about 4Oz(100g).
For a full head, 12-16 inch hair needs 2-3 packs, 18-24 inch needs 3-4 
packs, and above 24 inch needs a minimum of 4 packs.

name: Indian (5A Grade)
description: All the Indian hair is virgin hair whose tips are face the same direction, so they are definitely tangle free in the future. And the hair is full in the end. These high-quality strands have the entire cuticle intact, preventing tangling. Our Indian hair extensions are original straight, wavy or curly in texture.

name: Brazilian(5A Grade)
description:
100% Virgin Brazilian Hair. Hair holds curls really well. This texture blends well with relaxed hair. Hair comes in a natural black/brown color. Hair can be dyed, washed, flat ironed and blow dried. 100% Tangle and Matte Free. 3.8-4oz.

*All hair comes in a natural black/brown color if you want your hair colored, you must first add the lengths and textures to your cart and then click on the OMBRE OR DYE tab to add the color to your order.

name: Peruvian(5A Grade)
description:
100% unprocessed virgin Peruvian wavy hair. Flat iron to achieve a straight look. Hair comes in a natural dark black/brown color. Hair blends well with normal, full or relaxed textures. Strong wefts. 100% Tangle and Matte Free. 3.8-4oz.

*All hair comes in a natural black/brown color if you want your hair colored, you must first add the lengths and textures to your cart and then click on the OMBRE OR DYE tab to add the color to your order.

name: Waist Shapers
description:
Are you ready to maximize your workout with a waist cinching garment? Take it to the gym or for a run outside and let it add impact to your healthy lifestyle routine. Here’s how it works. You wrap the band around your midsection. This action creates compression in your core, stimulating thermal activity and ramping up perspiration. This process allows toxins and impurities to exit the skin, while mobilizing fat cells. Put simply, the band helps ensure that your workout is working for you.

The band itself is constructed from a latex core with a soft cotton exterior and interior lining. It sits at your waist, extending to the upper abdominals. Two columns of hook-and-eye closures allow you to size the garment down with you. Felix-Boning anchors the cincher and prevents migration.

YOU CAN EXERCISE IN THIS GARMENT!

IF UNSURE OF SIZE.. ORDER SHIRT SIZE.
